# Git Identity - Dirtybird (COMPANY ACCOUNT)

Dirtybird uses a SEPARATE company GitHub account, not the personal one.

## Before ANY git operation (commit, push, pull, clone):
```powershell
git config user.email
# MUST show: rdomingues@pitcherco.com
# If it shows a different email, the gitconfig conditional includes may not be working.
```

## Before ANY GitHub CLI operation:
```powershell
gh auth status
# MUST show: rdominguesds
# If wrong account: gh auth switch --user rdominguesds
```

